# Line endings (LF)

- Always use **LF** (`\n`), never **CRLF** (`\r\n`), when creating or editing files.
- Do not change line endings to CRLF, even on Windows.
- Project enforcement: `.editorconfig` (`end_of_line = lf`) and `.gitattributes` (`eol=lf`).
